To install sfml graphics and sqlite3 libraries, execute the following commands:

sudo apt install libsfml-dev
sudo apt install libsqlite3-dev

To compile the game, write the following line in terminal:

g++ snake.cpp snake_test.cpp -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-system -lsqlite3 -o snake

To run the game, simply write:

./snake
